  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Feasibility and toxicity of haploidentical transplantation of CD3/CD19 depleted stem cells in
      combination with a toxicity reduced conditioning regimen or with standard conditioning
      regimens according to underlying disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
